<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Innovate with AI</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/innovate-styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                    <img src="/images/modulelogo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
                </a>
                <div class="title">
                    <h1>04</h1>
                    <h1>INNOVATE WITH AI</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/playerinfo">
                                <img src="<%= user.playerAvatar %>" alt="Icon" class="icon">
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="tabs">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-2">
                    <button class="button button-active" data-id="1">Step 1: Identify a Problem</button>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-2">
                    <button class="button" data-id="2">Step 2: Devise a Solution</button>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-2">
                    <button class="button" data-id="3">Step 3: Explore Alpaca</button>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-2">
                    <button class="button" data-id="4">Step 4: Prompt Engineering</button>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-2">
                    <button class="button" data-id="5">Step 5: Transform an Image</button>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-2">
                    <button class="button" data-id="6">Step 6: Submit your Idea</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content">

        <div id="content-1" class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 left-section">
                    <div class="box-wrapper">
                        <div class="box-design">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-2">
                                    <img src="/images/orientationlogo.gif" alt="">
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-10">
                                    <p>Imagine an educational system designed to perfection. A system that understands and caters to student needs, and delivers information in the most engaging and effective manner. What would such a system look like? <br> <br>

                                        On the right, we have listed several themes that relate to classrooms in general. Pick a theme of your choice and identify a problem area to work on. <br><br>
                                        
                                        Note: Some areas within each theme have already been identified. You are free to use one of them, or come up with your own.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>   
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="playerinput">
                        <input type="text" id="step-1-input" class="form-control" placeholder="Provide a tentative description of the problem that you identified.">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-6 right-section">
                    <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                                <h2 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                        <span>▼</span> Personalized Learning
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                            </div>
        
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>• How can educational content be tailored to fit the unique needs and preferences of each student?</p>
                                    <p>• What kind of personalized recommendations or guidance could enhance a student's learning journey?</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                                <h2 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                        <span>▶</span> Accessibility and Inclusion
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>• How can educational resources be made more accessible to students with disabilities?</p>
                                    <p>• What can we bridge language barriers in multicultural classrooms?</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                                <h2 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                        <span>▶</span> Engagement and Motivation
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>• How can we gamify the learning process to increase student engagement and motivation?</p>
                                    <p>• How can we provide real-time feedback and encouragement to keep students motivated?</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header" id="headingFour">
                                <h2 class="mb-0">
                                    <button class="btn btn-link btn-block text-left collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                        <span>▶</span> Assessment and Feedback
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p>• How can we provide more personalized and constructive feedback on student work?</p>
                                    <p>• How can we offer alternative forms of assessment beyond traditional exams?</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="submit-button">
                        <button id="step-1-submit" class="btn btn-warning">PROCEED</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="content-2" class="container-fluid hidden">
            <h1>Content ID 2</h1>
        </div>

        <div id="content-3" class="container-fluid hidden">
            <h1>Content ID 3</h1>
        </div>

        <div id="content-4" class="container-fluid hidden">
            <h1>Content ID 4</h1>
        </div>

        <div id="content-5" class="container-fluid hidden">
            <h1>Content ID 5</h1>
        </div>

        <div id="content-6" class="container-fluid hidden">
            <h1>Content ID 6</h1>
        </div>

    </section>

    <script>
        let activeButtonId = 1;

        function setActive(button) {
            var buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.button');
            buttons.forEach(function(btn) {
                btn.classList.remove('button-active');
            });

            button.classList.add('button-active');

            activeButtonId = button.getAttribute('data-id');

            var contents = document.querySelectorAll('.content .container-fluid');
            contents.forEach(function(content) {
                content.classList.add('hidden');
            });

            var activeContent = document.getElementById('content-' + activeButtonId);
            if (activeContent) {
                activeContent.classList.remove('hidden');
            }
        }

        document.querySelectorAll('.button').forEach(button => {
            button.addEventListener('click', function() {
                setActive(this);
            });
        });

        document.getElementById('step-1-submit').addEventListener('click', function() {
            const playerInput = document.getElementById('step-1-input').value;

            fetch('/innovate/step1', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                },
                body: JSON.stringify({ playerInput: playerInput })
            })
            .then(response => response.json())
            .then(data => {
                console.log('Success:', data);
            })
            .catch((error) => {
                console.error('Error:', error);
            });
        });
    </script>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    
</body>
</html>
